Package: test_susine
Title: Simulation Harness for SuSiNE Model Experiments
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Callahan", email = "mgc5166@psu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for configuring, launching, and evaluating large-scale
    simulation studies that compare SuSiE and SuSiNE sparse regression
    variants. Includes run-control builders, SLURM array generation,
    task-execution helpers, and tidy metric exports for downstream analysis.
